	(text_box "Double-check that none of the following are used for critical pull-ups/peripherals that could interfere with boot:\r\nGPIO 0 (Boot mode)\r\nGPIO 45 (Must be low for 3.3v flash)\nGPIO 46 (Must be low for download mode)\r\nGPIO 43 (UART mode - ESP rom logs)\nGPIO 44 (UART mode - ESP rom logs)"
